body.name: ivinta 3 Tier Bookshelf, White Marble Wood Bookcase with Gold Metal Pipe Frame, Home Décor Display Rack for Living Room, Modern Open Etagere Shelf Stand, Small Storage Organizer Shelf
features: Modern White Home Décor Bookshelf- This ivinta shelf continues the classic bookshelf design and breaks with the tradition industrial brown color choice. With a new color style, the combination of white marble shelves and powder gold metal pipe racks, which brings a modern art style to your home. Whether used as a bookshelf or a display stand, it can make the living room look bright and uncluttered.

Multipurpose Simple Décor Display Rack- 14 inches of shelf height is enough to hold your vinyl records and CDs. Use this storage unit as a hardbound books shelf, plants shelf, toys shelves, snacks shelf, memorabilia shelf. You can even use it as a showcase aquarium or display shelf. Of course, cats will love it too. Dimensions:12"D x 30"W x 38"H.

Durable and Sturdy Book Case- 3-tier open high-quality shelf matched with rough style of carbon steel water pipe and absolutely stable structure, strong and durable. Each shelf can hold up to 100lbs. The iron pipe adopts a special painting process to ensure that the powder gold will not fall off during use.

Safe Narrow Bookshelves Freestanding- This classic bookshelf features an anti-tipping metal buckle for safety. Horseshoe-shaped carbon steel feet for a bigger contact area. Floor/carpet pads protector provided. Ivinta Bookshelf will never shake like other cheap bookshelves.

Wood Shelves with Metal Pipe Frame- The shelves are MDF board veneered in white marble, retaining the visual and tactile effect of marble while being lighter in weight, which can move easily. The surface is waterproof and scratch-resistant and easy to clean, no need to worry about the dust. The minimalist design is perfectly suitable for various decoration styles. It can be placed in the living room, bedroom, bathroom, home office, dormitory, apartment and so on.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 12, 2022
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars More parts than expected
reviews.reviewText: I love the final look of this bookshelf, I use it for a coffee bar in the kitchen. It was easy to put together but had a lot more parts than I expected so it took me longer than I thought. The pipe is real metal and I’ve had no issues with paint peeling or chipping when putting it together. The only thing I found annoying was making sure the top u shape was straight. While tightening the sides it was never even so eventually I had to loosen one side and just push it on the ground to make it even. I would also recommend different furniture sticker pads for the bottom. I have laminate floors we plan on redoing so the pad being thin and possibly leaving marks is okay. But if you have floors you care about spend the few bucks and get thicker ones.
